c1eb1932c61e2994157a6637b","tid":24033,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做唔做飯腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係毒撚先可以一齊食</blockquote><br />\n唔係毒撚就唔使搵飯腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf121d9bf4105737e96569e5bbda2aa8fba32a15","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日成班fd係學校溫書 當中有熟亦有d冇咁熟<br />\n佢地本身話夜晚食飯 後尾話冇預我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我就自己一個人<br />\n真係好開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你好似唔多開心喎 唔緊要啦大學d friend 浮雲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我成日係學自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申final year"},{"pid":"fc1770a77188233e26339925168e922de6261667","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好enjoy 自己食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係有時去快餐嗰類鋪頭難搵位d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘅極限係食飯 ，接受唔到一個人打邊爐。有次見到個呀叔食吉野家邊爐 我直頭想撘枱一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd26637a473ff9dc5f9e432baeaa02ffff9b89d2","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好enjoy 自己食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係有時去快餐嗰類鋪頭難搵位d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時lunch時段，三個學生妹夾我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c10b78a0a3368d5ee1021d734bbc429a6529c31","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做唔做飯腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係毒撚先可以一齊食</blockquote><br />\n唔係毒撚就唔使搵飯腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒撚同毒撚食飯會有咩化學作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c8a0778a225dba895b043d7642b478bc592a71","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚食相好恐怖，特別係毒到不能自拔果班<br />\n今日見到個毒撚成隻河馬咁坐對面食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲唔毒食相都好唔掂，食啖飯都餓鬼搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd7dc3e0c54a103db7820f13c031dba37fbfdd8","tid":24033,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>毒撚食相好恐怖，特別係毒到不能自拔果班<br />\n今日見到個毒撚成隻河馬咁坐對面食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲唔毒食相都好唔掂，食啖飯都餓鬼搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到佢個食相我半碟都未食到就想嘔<br />\n飲凍檸茶都嚇到粒檸檬核KICK左係喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b738c5d0400f720d42ad3d95b6f2c1e07ebb0dc","tid":24033,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wD140Or.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwD140Or.jpg&h=37bacc96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13445b69712e90f2b6abe737aca72c4de90aa776","tid":24033,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;做唔做飯腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係毒撚先可以一齊食&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n唔係毒撚就唔使搵飯腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n毒撚同毒撚食飯會有咩化學作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長期一個人食唔慌無化學作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9176910f5fc6e29b869d4c754ed455f0e6064e36","tid":24033,"uid":21934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"冇撚點做毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea5dc5bf4f9d327d333e10f616b8a59a95252c6","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>毒撚食相好恐怖，特別係毒到不能自拔果班<br />\n今日見到個毒撚成隻河馬咁坐對面食lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲唔毒食相都好唔掂，食啖飯都餓鬼搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到佢個食相我半碟都未食到就想嘔<br />\n飲凍檸茶都嚇到粒檸檬核KICK左係喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有沒咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5497a5490b8dd83e5a21dcf7a686743bb4974b4e","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wD140Or.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwD140Or.jpg&h=37bacc96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d6b97c3342d0ac212aeabd05fd23a9b1c64402","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;做唔做飯腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係毒撚先可以一齊食&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n唔係毒撚就唔使搵飯腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&amp;lt;/blockquote&amp;gt;<br />\n<br />\n毒撚同毒撚食飯會有咩化學作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n長期一個人食唔慌無化學作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 腐爛"},{"pid":"c4d7340cf81fe6a11500730aca9c9864e46df118","tid":24033,"uid":9322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇撚點做毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毒西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a0324cbba16f6a0ab4d0d40bb62dec9957d8dc","tid":24033,"uid":3226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識乜嘢，有時要好好享受自己獨處時間，有女都有好多嘢煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>都係，低質社交不如高質獨處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>但有時會好孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>所有間唔中要搵女傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我都係比較嚮往一個人嘅時間，乜都唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>係咪好多男人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得傾下計冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea19499f657cd